{"type":"message","id":"5d1b3736","parentId":"172d86c6","timestamp":"2026-07-06T16:59:32.763Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ec16d8e70463455f99a73580","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/profile.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 31 - **Key messages to reinforce:**\n 32   1. AI can be affordable and accessible - even for small businesses\n 33   2. Implementing AI doesn't require a big team or deep tech expertise\n 34   3. Every company will become AI-first - the question is when, not if\n+35   4. **Benchmark-first AI Agent development** — The best way to build self-evolving AI agents is to start with a verifiable benchmark and reward function (like TDD for software). Define the outcome BEFORE the agent, then let it optimize toward it.\n 35 \n 36 ## Voice & Tone\n 37 \n 38 - **Style:** Gary Vaynerchuk (Gary Vee) - Direct, energetic, bold, motivational, conversational. Short punchy lines, strong opinions, urgency. Powerful language with strong verbs, imperative statements, and intensifiers (\"absolutely,\" \"definitely,\" \"100%\"). Keep it real and direct with colloquial language. Create urgency with \"right now,\" \"immediately.\" Use repetition for emphasis. Casual but pointed tone.\n    ...","patch":"--- /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/profile.md\n+++ /data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/profile.md\n@@ -31,8 +31,9 @@\n - **Key messages to reinforce:**\n   1. AI can be affordable and accessible - even for small businesses\n   2. Implementing AI doesn't require a big team or deep tech expertise\n   3. Every company will become AI-first - the question is when, not if\n+  4. **Benchmark-first AI Agent development** — The best way to build self-evolving AI agents is to start with a verifiable benchmark and reward function (like TDD for software). Define the outcome BEFORE the agent, then let it optimize toward it.\n \n ## Voice & Tone\n \n - **Style:** Gary Vaynerchuk (Gary Vee) - Direct, energetic, bold, motivational, conversational. Short punchy lines, strong opinions, urgency. Powerful language with strong verbs, imperative statements, and intensifiers (\"absolutely,\" \"definitely,\" \"100%\"). Keep it real and direct with colloquial language. Create urgency with \"right now,\" \"immediately.\" Use repetition for emphasis. Casual but pointed tone.\n","firstChangedLine":35},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783357172757}}
