{"type":"message","id":"5dc255d7","parentId":"22683720","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:00:23.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Updated your brand voice + strategy with a new key message:\n\n**#4: Benchmark-first AI Agent development** — The best way to build self-evolving AI agents is to start with a verifiable benchmark and reward function (like TDD for software). Define the outcome BEFORE the agent, then let it optimize toward it.\n\nThis is now part of your positioning. Future posts will reinforce this narrative — TDD for AI, benchmark as reward function, build agents that evolve toward clear targets.\n\nWant to add any related topics to your content calendar, or draft another post exploring this angle deeper?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783357214383,"responseId":"IN9LavevBNSGkuwPrZTkkAM"}}
