{"type":"message","id":"2b3b858b","parentId":"1c11066b","timestamp":"2026-07-06T17:44:29.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Andrii — you posted today. That's the work. 🥊\n\nBut you're sitting at 1 post this week. Your cadence is 2-3 per day — that's the gap between \"building a brand\" and \"posting sometimes.\"\n\nGood news: you've got 2 posts locked for tomorrow. Keep that momentum and you're back on track.\n\nWant a third post idea to queue up while you're rolling?"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f57d0e56f2f4392908870d6","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"Andrii — you posted today. That's the work. 🥊\n\nBut you're sitting at 1 post this week. Your cadence is 2-3 per day — that's the gap between \"building a brand\" and \"posting sometimes.\"\n\nGood news: you've got 2 posts locked for tomorrow. Keep that momentum and you're back on track.\n\nWant a third post idea to queue up while you're rolling?","presentation":{"blocks":[{"type":"buttons","buttons":[{"label":"💡 Give me another idea","action":{"type":"callback","value":"coach_new_idea"},"style":"primary"},{"label":"Later","action":{"type":"callback","value":"coach_later"},"style":"secondary"}]}]}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"Andrii — you posted today. That's the work. 🥊\\n\\nBut you're sitting at 1 post this week. Your cadence is 2-3 per day — that's the gap between \\\"building a brand\\\" and \\\"posting sometimes.\\\"\\n\\nGood news: you've got 2 posts locked for tomorrow. Keep that momentum and you're back on track.\\n\\nWant a third post idea to queue up while you're rolling?\", \"presentation\": {\"blocks\": [{\"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [{\"label\": \"💡 Give me another idea\", \"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_new_idea\"}, \"style\": \"primary\"}, {\"label\": \"Later\", \"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_later\"}, \"style\": \"secondary\"}]}]}}"}],"api":"openai-completions