{"type":"message","id":"4c3424d1","parentId":"2cd08db0","timestamp":"2026-07-06T18:14:26.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Andrii — you posted today. That's the work. 💪\n\nBut your target is 2-3 posts per day. One post this week won't build the brand you want.\n\nGood news: you've got 2 scheduled for tomorrow on the benchmark-first AI agent series. That's momentum building.\n\nKeep it going. Want me to draft 1-2 more posts for tomorrow to hit your cadence?"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bed95276396344b7918a2620","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\"lastChecks\":{\"linkedin_daily_brief\":1783318444,\"linkedin_coach\":1783360788,\"linkedin_trends_flagged\":null}}","path":"/data/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"},"partialArgs":"{\"content\": \"{\\\"lastChecks\\\":{\\\"linkedin_daily_brief\\\":1783318444,\\\"linkedin_coach\\\":1783360788,\\\"linkedin_trends_flagged\\\":null}}\", \"path\": \"/data/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783361656267,"responseId":"evBLapK3DsfKwOYP6KGRmAY"}}
