{"type":"message","id":"66d13dcf","parentId":"c0a332c2","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:44:13.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_234d7431bcec4a4bb13d9a83","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nFLAG=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/.brief-sent-$TODAY\"\n[ -f \"$FLAG\" ] && echo \"BRIEF_SENT=true\" || echo \"BRIEF_SENT=false\"\necho \"TODAY=$TODAY\"\ndate +%H"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\\nFLAG=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/.brief-sent-$TODAY\\\"\\n[ -f \\\"$FLAG\\\" ] && echo \\\"BRIEF_SENT=true\\\" || echo \\\"BRIEF_SENT=false\\\"\\necho \\\"TODAY=$TODAY\\\"\\ndate +%H\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b380932cb5974ff9839d452d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/content-calendar.md","limit":20,"offset":55},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/content-calendar.md\", \"limit\": 20, \"offset\": 55}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783381441549,"responseId":"wz1MaqvgIIqM6dgPkLuekAM"}}
{"type":"message","id":"59c9356e","parentId":"66d13dcf","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:44:13.581Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_234d7431bcec4a4bb13d9a83","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"BRIEF_SENT=true\nTODAY=2026-07-06\n23"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"BRIEF_SENT=true\nTODAY=2026-07-06\n23","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783381453579}}
{"type":"message","id":"f017f5aa","parentId":"59c9356e","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:44:13.585Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b380932cb5974ff9839d452d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nThis is the drift problem. Most agents have no anchor. They optimize for whatever feels right in the moment — but there's no fixed target.\n\nThe fix: **benchmark + reward function.**\n\nDefine the outcome. Make it measurable. Let the agent optimize toward it.\n\nEvery successful iteration is progress. Every failure is a signal. No guessing.\n\nTraditional software has tests. AI agents need benchmarks.\n\nWithout one, you're not building a system. You're building a feeling.\n\nWhat's your agent's benchmark — or are you hoping it figures itself out?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #MachineLearning #SoftwareEngineering #TDD\n\n**Characters:** ~900\n\n---\n\n[67 more lines in file. Use offset=75 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783381453584}}
