{"type":"message","id":"27fb63b1","parentId":"19c86d32","timestamp":"2026-07-07T00:14:54.921Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good morning! ☀️\n\nYou're crushing it — **10 posts this week**, posted yesterday, and **2 posts are already queued to auto-publish today** (9 AM and 3 PM UTC).\n\nBoth reinforce your new **benchmark-first AI agent** narrative. They'll drop automatically — I'll ping you with the URLs once they're live.\n\nNo action needed. Keep the momentum. 🚀"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d9ad4ed4250a44e298dfcf69","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"Good morning, Andrii! ☀️\n\nYou're crushing it — 10 posts this week, posted yesterday, and 2 posts are already queued to auto-publish today (9 AM and 3 PM UTC).\n\nBoth reinforce your new benchmark-first AI agent narrative. They'll drop automatically — I'll ping you with the URLs once they're live.\n\nNo action needed. Keep the momentum. 🚀","target":"264468965"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"Good morning, Andrii! ☀️\\n\\nYou're crushing it — 10 posts this week, posted yesterday, and 2 posts are already queued to auto-publish today (9 AM and 3 PM UTC).\\n\\nBoth reinforce your new benchmark-first AI agent narrative. They'll drop automatically — I'll ping you with the URLs once they're live.\\n\\nNo action needed. Keep the momentum. 🚀\", \"target\": \"264468965\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783383288119,"responseId":"-kRMatTrBb-S6dgPqeLdoAI"}}
